text: Oedudes bifasciata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Henry Walter Bates in 1869.http://copa.acguanacaste.ac.cr:8080/bitstream/handle/11606/308/CostaRicaCerambycidae2010%20copia.pdf?sequence=1&isAllowed;=y It is known from Panama, Honduras,http://files.frardonr.webnode.es/200002404-6f0aa70040/ESTUDIO%20DIVERSIDAD%20BIOLOGICA%20DE%20LA%20RESERVA%20BIOLOGICA%20EL%20CHILE,%20HONDURAS.pdf Costa Rica and Nicaragua.BioLib.cz - Oedudes bifasciata.
